---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Sell Your Home"
  description="Sell your San Diego home for top dollar with Rusty Rau. Expert marketing, strategic pricing, and skilled negotiation to maximize your home's value."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="page-hero sellers-hero">
    <div class="hero-background">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600607687939-ce8a6c25118c?w=1920&q=80" alt="Luxury home interior" class="hero-image" loading="eager">
      <div class="hero-overlay dark"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <span class="hero-tag">For Sellers</span>
      <h1 class="hero-title">Sell Your Home<br><span class="accent">For Top Dollar</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Strategic marketing, expert pricing, and skilled negotiation to maximize your home's value in the San Diego market.</p>
      <div class="hero-cta-group">
        <a href="/contact" class="cta-button pulse-glow">Get Your Home's Value</a>
        <a href="/#testimonials" class="cta-button secondary">See Results</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Intro Section -->
  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="intro-content">
        <h2 class="section-title">Your Home Deserves Better Than Average</h2>
        <p class="lead-text">
          Selling your home is one of the biggest financial decisions you'll ever make. The difference between an average agent and the right agent can mean tens of thousands of dollars—and months of unnecessary stress.
        </p>
        <p>
          I don't just list homes. I create comprehensive marketing strategies designed to showcase your property to qualified buyers, generate competitive offers, and negotiate the best possible terms. Every home I represent gets my full attention, personalized approach, and commitment to excellence.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Choose Me Section -->
  <section class="content-section alt-bg">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-tag center">The Difference</span>
      <h2 class="section-title center">Why Sellers Choose Rusty</h2>
      
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i></div>
          <h3>Strategic Pricing</h3>
          <p>Pricing your home correctly from day one is critical. I analyze comparable sales, market trends, and your home's unique features to position your property for maximum value.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-camera"></i></div>
          <h3>Professional Marketing</h3>
          <p>Your home will be showcased with professional photography, compelling descriptions, targeted digital advertising, and exposure across all major platforms.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-handshake"></i></div>
          <h3>Expert Negotiation</h3>
          <p>When offers come in, I leverage my experience to negotiate not just the highest price, but the best terms—protecting your interests through closing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-comments"></i></div>
          <h3>Constant Communication</h3>
          <p>You'll never wonder what's happening with your listing. I provide regular updates, showing feedback, market insights, and am always just a call away.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-home"></i></div>
          <h3>Local Expertise</h3>
          <p>Born and raised in San Diego, I know this market inside and out. I understand what makes each area special and how to market your home accordingly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-clipboard-check"></i></div>
          <h3>Seamless Process</h3>
          <p>From preparing your home for market through closing day, I coordinate every detail—staging, inspections, repairs, paperwork, and timelines.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Process Section -->
  <section class="content-section process-section">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-tag center">The Process</span>
      <h2 class="section-title center">How I Sell Your Home</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">A proven approach to get you the best results</p>
      
      <div class="process-timeline">
        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="step-number">01</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Consultation & Strategy</h3>
            <ul class="step-list">
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Walk through your home together</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Discuss your goals and timeline</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Analyze comparable sales and market conditions</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Develop a customized pricing strategy</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="step-number">02</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Preparation & Staging</h3>
            <ul class="step-list">
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Professional staging consultation</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Recommendations for repairs or improvements</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Professional photography and videography</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Compelling listing description</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="step-number">03</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Marketing & Exposure</h3>
            <ul class="step-list">
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> MLS listing with maximum exposure</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Featured on all major real estate websites</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Targeted digital advertising campaigns</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Open houses and broker tours</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="step-number">04</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Showings & Feedback</h3>
            <ul class="step-list">
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Coordinate and schedule all showings</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Collect and share buyer feedback</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Weekly updates on activity and interest</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Adjust strategy as needed</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="step-number">05</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Offers & Negotiation</h3>
            <ul class="step-list">
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Review and analyze all offers</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Verify buyer qualifications</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Strategic counter-offer negotiation</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Manage multiple offer situations</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="step-number">06</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Escrow & Closing</h3>
            <ul class="step-list">
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Coordinate with escrow, title, and lender</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Manage inspections and negotiations</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Final walk-through coordination</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Smooth closing and key transfer</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonial Highlight -->
  <section class="testimonial-highlight">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="highlight-card">
        <div class="quote-icon"><i class="fas fa-quote-left"></i></div>
        <p class="highlight-text">"Rusty has the expertise, knowledge and motivation to make your buying/selling needs go better than you expect! I'm not kidding! I was truly blessed to have found Rusty to help me with my home sale."</p>
        <div class="highlight-author">
          <span class="author-name">Paul S.</span>
          <span class="author-detail">Sold a home in Mira Costa, Oceanside</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <h2>Ready to Sell Your Home?</h2>
      <p>Schedule a complimentary consultation. I'll provide a detailed market analysis and customized strategy for your home.</p>
      <div class="contact-cta-info">
        <a href="tel:+18582044692" class="contact-link"><i class="fas fa-phone"></i> (858) 204-4692</a>
        <a href="mailto:rusty@rauhomegroup.com" class="contact-link"><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> rusty@rauhomegroup.com</a>
      </div>
      <a href="/contact" class="cta-button">Get Your Home's Value</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .contact-cta-info {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  
  .contact-link {
    color: var(--color-white);
    text-decoration: none;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .contact-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-gold);
  }
  
  /* Fix scroll animation glitch on sellers hero */
  .sellers-hero .hero-background {
    position: absolute;
    will-change: auto;
    transform: none !important;
  }
  
  .sellers-hero .hero-image {
    will-change: auto;
    transform: none !important;
    backface-visibility: hidden;
  }
  
  .sellers-hero .hero-content {
    will-change: auto;
    transform: none !important;
  }
  
  .sellers-hero .hero-overlay {
    will-change: auto;
  }
</style>
